responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "4EC3A1E14CBA6AD254CDA3843F7180A5", "This appears to be a horrible attempt at goblin war logistics. The writer of these orders seems confused about which goblin is their warchieftain between three: Nurz in the west camp, Gibbok in the central camp and Klin in the east camp. It is likely not the only such document in existence.")
name: DD_0023_RealGoblinCorrespondance_2
